Trans World Specialties
Wherever We Fly, We Have the Enviable Opportunity to Taste
and Savor the Cuisines of Each Land. You are Invited to
Share Some of Our All Time Favorites.
SALISBURY STEAK BORDELAISE
An American favorite! A hearty grilled U.S. choice
chopped beef steak topped with a mushroom wine sauce.
Presented with O'Brien potatoes and parsley whole carrots.
CHICKEN BREAST NEW ENGLAND
A Partially Boned Breast of Chicken
with a Traditional New England Stuffing
of Bread Crumbs, Apples, Celery, Onions
and Seasonings... Complemented by Sauce
Supreme, and Served with Au Gratin
Potatoes and Green Peas with Pimentos.
SEAFOOD NEWBURG
Poached Fillet of Sole, Tender Scallops
and Shrimp in a Sherry Flavored Sauce.
Accompanied by a Nest of Buttered Rice
and Green Beans Amandine.
Please accept our apologies
if your choice is not available on this flight.
